channel.title: 508 run problem
channel.description:
hi, i just decided to start a server, but when i do, i get this:
Now starting Drowning508... Please wait...
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: src/palidino76/rs2/Se rver Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: src.palidino76.rs2.Server at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(URLClassLoader.java:202) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(URLClassLoader.java:190) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:307) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Launcher.java:301) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:248) Could not find the main class: src/palidino76/rs2/Server. Program will exit. Press any key to continue . . . now im not asking for spoonfeeding, i tried everything in my knowledge, and i dont think google would have this exact thing.... maybe showing my post... anyways i checked the directory its leading to, there is server.java there!
